Title: The Usurper
Plot: The fleet returns to Kattegat to find tragic circumstances await. Lagertha learns that her Earldom has been usurped and convinces Ragnar to travel to Hederby with her in an effort to reclaim her title. Ragnar causes great surprise when he announces the next raid. The Seer has interesting prophecies for Rollo.
GuestStars: Moe Dunford, Maude Hirst, Gaia Weiss, Jennie Jacques, John Kavanagh
